31:17.690 --> 31:20.682
to_ one of those motels
like you took me to.

31:20.690 --> 31:22.373
-Oh my god, I'm so sorry.

31:22.380 --> 31:29.889
-No, no, no, that's not-- I
didn't-- he just got really

31:29.890 --> 31:35.351
mean, and then he- sort
of had me on the ground.

31:35.360 --> 31:37.954
