32:12.570 --> 32:19.601
That, you know, he was on some
secret classified mission.

32:19.610 --> 32:21.896
No one could get
access to his files.

32:21.900 --> 32:24.209
They just sort of buried them.

32:24.220 --> 32:25.585
-Assholes.

32:25.590 --> 32:26.284
-Ugh.

32:26.290 --> 32:27.211
I don't know why I told you.

32:27.220 --> 32:28.790
I'm so sorry.

32:28.800 --> 32:37.970
I-- you just-- seem nice.

32:37.980 --> 32:39.641
And not like the rest of them.

32:43.220 --> 32:45.575
-I'm so sorry.

32:45.580 --> 32:50.415
I wish, I wish, there
was something I could do.

32:50.420 --> 32:51.648
-No, there's nothing.

32:51.660 --> 32:56.142
I-- believe me, I've
tried everything.

32:56.150 --> 32:58.539
