32:58.550 --> 32:59.357
-Do you know his name?

33:06.250 --> 33:08.707
-Larrick.

33:08.710 --> 33:11.656
Andrew.

33:11.660 --> 33:16.097
I think he's a
captain or something.

33:16.100 --> 33:19.729
-I know where his files are.

33:19.740 --> 33:20.820
-You do?

33:20.830 --> 33:23.321
-It wouldn't be easy,
but I could get them.

33:23.330 --> 33:25.207
