lawyer, prove he was there.

33:25.210 --> 33:27.189
-No, I wouldn't want you
to do that, because what

33:27.200 --> 33:29.418
if someone saw you taking them?

33:29.420 --> 33:30.853
-I don't have to take them.

33:30.860 --> 33:31.804
I could copy them.

33:36.050 --> 33:36.744
-Nothing much.

33:36.750 --> 33:40.242
We're, uh, we're having a
long, lazy romantic morning.

33:40.250 --> 33:42.980
I know.

33:42.990 --> 33:46.585
You know once in awhile, you and
daddy should just-- no, really.

33:46.590 --> 33:49.343
You should.

33:49.350 --> 33:51.159
Romance is so important.

33:51.160 --> 33:54.061
Could I call you back,
mom, just a couple minutes.

33:54.070 --> 33:57.528
OK, bye.

33:57.530 --> 34:01.136
Hey, why are you all spiffed up?

34:01.140 --> 34:04.530
What happened to our
lazy, romantic morning?

34:04.540 --> 34:05.757
-Thought we had it.

34:05.760 --> 34:06.897
-Um we had the start of it.

34:06.900 --> 34:08.697
-Yeah, and then you got on
the phone with your mother,

34:08.700 --> 34:10.053
like you always do.

34:10.060 --> 34:12.688
-Hey, I thought you
loved my mother.

34:12.690 --> 34:14.794
-Martha, we have so little
time together as it is,

34:14.800 --> 34:16.859
whenever we manage to squeeze
out just a little extra,

34:16.870 --> 34:19.350
you get on the phone
with your mother.

34:19.360 --> 34:20.088
-She called me.

34:20.090 --> 34:22.365
-So tell her to call back.

34:22.370 --> 34:23.962
Why should I sit around
twiddling my thumbs,

34:23.970 --> 34:25.130
while you talk with your mom?

34:25.140 --> 34:26.209
-Twiddling your thumbs?

34:26.220 --> 34:28.040
Is that what you call it
when we're lying here,

34:28.050 --> 34:29.199
cuddly and warm?

34:29.210 --> 34:31.599
-There is nothing for
me to do while you're

34:31.610 --> 34:33.009
on the phone with your mother.

34:33.010 --> 34:35.092
This isn't my home.

34:35.100 --> 34:36.169
-This is your home.

34:36.170 --> 34:37.614
Well, I-- I'm not
going to intrude.

34:37.620 --> 34:38.814
I'm luclq I have
half a sock drawer.

34:38.820 --> 34:39.718
-Do you want a sock drawer?

34:39.720 --> 34:40.778
