37:35.580 --> 37:37.002
-Oh.

37:37.010 --> 37:37.829
-Are you mad at me?

37:37.840 --> 37:39.626
I'm sorry.

37:39.630 --> 37:40.528
-No.

37:40.530 --> 37:41.258
That's OK.

37:41.260 --> 37:46.323
I-- it was a lot to hope for.

37:46.330 --> 37:48.525
I've probably seen too
many movies, you know.

37:48.530 --> 37:54.582
You meet a guy and you think--
ha, you found your hero.

37:54.590 --> 37:56.478
I was stupid.

37:56.490 --> 37:59.152
Who thinks that way?

37:59.160 --> 38:00.957
-It was just so rislq.

