38:02.970 --> 38:05.336
What am I doing this for?

38:05.340 --> 38:06.034
I'm sorry.

38:06.040 --> 38:07.223
It's making me so tense.

38:14.210 --> 38:15.404
-I could help you with that.

38:26.790 --> 38:28.269
-Oh you don't have to.

38:34.220 --> 38:37.189
-That's better right?

38:37.190 --> 38:38.669
That's better.

38:38.670 --> 38:40.365
-Oh, Jesus Christ.

38:40.370 --> 38:41.064
-That's better.

40:00.830 --> 40:01.899
-Here you go.

40:01.910 --> 40:02.592
-Thanks.

40:05.150 --> 40:06.117
OK, so.

40:18.200 --> 40:18.894
-Amen.

40:23.910 --> 40:24.831
Please pass the chicken.

41:13.280 --> 41:14.212
-Clark, are you there?

41:14.220 --> 41:15.141
Pick up.

41:18.430 --> 41:20.500
Your wife.

41:20.510 --> 41:23.479
Who are you?

41:23.480 --> 41:28.656
I know you can't tell me, ever.

41:28.660 --> 41:31.151
We need to talk, Clark.

41:31.160 --> 41:31.854
Call me.

41:53.040 --> 41:54.769
-She was praying, Phillip.

41:54.770 --> 41:56.032
Praying.

41:56.040 --> 41:59.146
If she just wants to say grace,
that's all it is, I think--

41:59.150 --> 41:59.844
-It's not.

41:59.850 --> 42:01.078
This is what happens.

42:01.090 --> 42:02.443
They get them when
they're children,

42:02.450 --> 42:05.385
