with friendship, and songs,

42:05.390 --> 42:06.971
and cute boys
cooing about Jesus.

42:06.980 --> 42:07.674
-So?

42:07.680 --> 42:09.136
Maybe it's crush.

42:09.140 --> 42:11.188
-Did you see any signs
of this while I was gone?

42:11.190 --> 42:12.885
-No.

42:12.890 --> 42:14.255
-We haven't been paying
enough attention.

42:14.260 --> 42:15.545
-Yes, we have.

42:15.550 --> 42:17.074
There's been kind of a
lot going on, you know?

42:17.080 --> 42:19.173
-If we'd been paying attention,
this would have happened.

42:19.180 --> 42:20.442
The lying?

42:20.450 --> 42:22.315
-Yeah, that's not like her.

42:22.320 --> 42:24.151
-I mean, you protect
them from the big things

42:24.160 --> 42:26.185
out there, the, the big
life and death dangers,

42:26.190 --> 42:28.750
and then something finds
its way into your house.

42:28.750 --> 42:30.308
-Look, we don't
know anything yet.

42:30.320 --> 42:31.469
Kids go through phases.

42:31.480 --> 42:32.663
Let's keep an eye on it.

42:32.670 --> 42:33.921
-No, that's how this happened.

42:33.930 --> 42:36.740
We let our guard down.

42:36.750 --> 42:40.550
Phillip, you and I
we know who we are.

42:40.560 --> 42:41.538
We have values.

42:41.540 --> 42:44.282
But these kids,
what do they know?

42:44.290 --> 42:44.984
We're failing them.

42:44.990 --> 42:46.082
-We're not failing them.

42:46.090 --> 42:47.682
-We're failing to
help them stand up

42:47.690 --> 42:50.762
to the distractions,
the consumerism.

42:50.770 --> 42:52.351
Look at this country.

42:52.360 --> 42:53.566
Church, synagogue,
I mean, that's

42:53.570 --> 42:54.502
what's holding it all up.

42:54.510 --> 42:56.284
The opiate of the masses.

42:56.290 --> 42:58.815
-Let's eat later tomorrow.

42:58.820 --> 42:59.730
-What?

42:59.740 --> 43:01.014
-We at dinner early tonight.

43:01.020 --> 43:02.840
