43:45.100 --> 43:46.874
I just have no choice.

43:46.880 --> 43:48.586
I'm putting your
name down, Clark.

43:48.590 --> 43:50.808
You're my husband
and it's the truth.

43:50.810 --> 43:51.504
Call me!

43:59.460 --> 44:00.154
-It's late.

44:00.160 --> 44:01.149
